{"word":"Dead Sea","slug":"dead-sea","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Dead Sea</b> Lies southeast of Jerusalem.<br/> Called Salt Sea<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=14&verse=3'>Gen 14:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=34&verse=12'>Num 34:12</a><br/> Called Sea of the Plain<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=3&verse=17'>Deu 3:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=4&verse=49'>Deu 4:49</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=3&verse=16'>Jos 3:16</a><br/> Called East Sea<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=2&verse=20'>Joe 2:20</a><br/> Called Former Sea<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=14&verse=8'>Zec 14:8</a><br/> Prophecy concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=47&verse=10'>Eze 47:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=47&verse=18'>Eze 47:18</a>"}]}